Round 5 features implemented:

FEAT-1: Shared SSRF module — app/core/security/ssrf.py
  resolve_and_pin_url() (async) and resolve_and_pin_url_sync() (sync)
  Single DNS pass: resolves once, validates ALL returned IPs, pins URL to first resolved IP.
  Eliminates TOCTOU window (DNS rebinding, CWE-918) across ALL 6 SSRF call sites:
    - app/modules/agents/a2a_proxy.py       (pinned_endpoint → httpx)
    - app/modules/agents/mcp_client.py      (verify_and_enumerate + call_tool)
    - app/modules/agents/a2a_card_fetcher.py (require_https=True)
    - app/modules/agents/a2a_health_worker.py
    - app/modules/tools/executor.py          (HttpWrapperExecutor + McpSseExecutor)
    - app/modules/platform/llm_library/routes.py (_assert_endpoint_ssrf_safe delegates)
  SSRF_BLOCKED_NETWORKS canonical blocklist: RFC1918, loopback, link-local, CGNAT,
    Azure Wire Server, IPv6 ULA, class E reserved.
  SSRFBlockedError: machine-readable .code; details logged server-side only.
  Fixes HIGH-1 (DNS rebinding TOCTOU across 6 of 7 SSRF implementations).

FEAT-2: BYOLLM key rotation UI
  New file: src/web/app/settings/llm-profile/elements/RotateKeyModal.tsx
    Password input (min 8 chars, DM Mono), warn-coloured confirmation notice,
    1.2s green success state, inline error surfacing. Enter submits, Escape closes.
  Modified: src/web/app/settings/llm-profile/elements/BYOLLMSection.tsx
    KeyRound icon button per slot, refetch() after successful rotation.
  Fixes VA-M2 (BYOLLM key rotation hook existed, no UI wired up).

FEAT-3: Cost analytics routes — fixes COST-1 (inline "Failed to load" on cost page)
  GET /api/v1/platform/analytics/cost/summary
    Aggregate: total_llm_cost, total_infra_cost, total_revenue, gross_margin_pct, period.
    Infra cost = INFRA_COST_PER_TENANT_DAILY_USD (env, default $1.50) × tenants × days.
    gross_margin_pct = None when revenue is zero (starter tenants).
  GET /api/v1/platform/analytics/cost/tenants
    Per-tenant breakdown with plan, tokens_consumed, costs, revenue, margin.
  GET /api/v1/platform/analytics/cost/margin-trend
    Date-series [{date, margin_pct}] from cost_summary_daily. Empty list when no data.

FEAT-4: LLM Profile version history and rollback — fixes VA-C1 (PA-4 feature gap)
  GET /api/v1/platform/llm-profiles/{id}/history
    Reads llm_profile_audit_log newest-first; limit param (1–100, default 20).
    Verifies profile is platform-owned (no BYOLLM bleed).
  POST /api/v1/platform/llm-profiles/{id}/rollback/{history_id}
    Extracts diff.before slot fields (allowlisted to *_library_id, *_params, *_traffic_split).
    Returns 422 if diff.before has no slot fields (e.g., create entries).
    Writes rollback audit entry with rolled_back_from_history_id.
    Calls resolver.invalidate_all() after commit.
  Hooks: useProfileHistory + useRollbackProfile in usePlatformLLMProfiles.ts
  UI: Collapsible "Version History" section in ProfileDetailPanel.tsx
    Action badge (DM Mono 10px), relative timestamps, Rollback button with
    warn-dim confirmation treatment.

